Class Booking

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.bot.spring.Booking
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subject

    public class Booking
extends java.lang.Object
implements Subject

    Booking details, mainly depend on a Tour object, Date object and other related information

    The Booking class stores the details of the booking made during the conversation of the client and the bot
